Country Music News International Newsletter April 17. 2017 Here is your Country Music News of the day from Country Music News International Magazine http://countrymusicnewsinternational.blogspot.com . Your Country Music News is supported by Nashville Convention Center & Visitors Bureau (Visit Music City), Tenessee Tourism (Entdecke Tennessee), Eileen Carey, Jaehl, Coreopsis Publications LLC (Coffeeshop Blues), Gestüt St. Georg Kilianstädten, Versicherungsmakler Jacob, Il Sorriso Cocktail Lounge Bar, The Independent Music Show", USA Songwriting Competition, Unsigned Only, Pyramid Sun Sonnenstudio, Kriz Rogers, Stella Tabelon ... 
You can publish the Newsletter to your websites or forward to your friends. If you want to publish some of the interviews, please contact me. 
Country Music News: 
Jake Worthington on Country Music News International Radio Show April 19. + 21. + 22. + 23. interviewed by Christian Lamitschka http://countrymusicnewsinternational.blogspot.de/2017/04/jake-worthington-on-country-music-news.html
